19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 85.59 of Title 74, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 A. As used in this act:
22 1. “Company” means any sole proprietorship, organization,
23 association, corporation, partnership, joint venture, limited
24 partnership, limited liability partnership, limited liability
